<font size=5>Research</font>
<hr/>
<ul>
<li><b> Rigidity and Tolerance in point processes: Gaussian zeroes and Ginibre eigenvalues</b><i>, with Y. Peres,</i><br /> <i>Duke Mathematical Journal, to appear</i><br /><a  target="_blank" href="http://arxiv.org/abs/1211.2381">preprint</a></li>
<br>
<li><b> Determinantal processes and completeness of random exponentials: the critical case </b><i><br /> Probability Theory and Related Fields, to appear</i><br><a  target="_blank" href="http://arxiv.org/abs/1211.2435">preprint</a></li>
<br>
<li><b>Large deviations for zeros of random polynomials with i.i.d. exponential coefficients</b>,<i> with O. Zeitouni,<br /> Int. Math. Res. Not., to appear </i><br><a  target="_blank" href="http://arxiv.org/abs/1312.6195">preprint</a></li>
<br>
<li><b>Continuum Percolation for Gaussian zeroes and Ginibre eigenvalues</b><i>, with M. Krishnapur and Y. Peres,</i><br />Annals of Probability, to appear <br> <a  target="_blank" href="http://arxiv.org/abs/1211.2514">preprint</a></li>
<br>
<li><b>Symmetry of Bound and Antibound States in the Semiclassical Limit for a General Class of Potentials</b><i>, with S. Dyatlov,<br />Proc. Amer. Math. Soc. 138 (2010), 3203-3210 </i><br /><a  target="_blank" href="http://arxiv.org/abs/0911.4282">preprint</a></li>
<br>
<li><b>Exact quantum algorithm to distinguish Boolean functions of different weights </b><i>, with S.L. Braunstein, B.S. Choi and S. Maitra, <br />Journal of Physics A: Mathematical and Theoretical, Volume 40, Number 29 </i><br /><a  target="_blank" href="http://iopscience.iop.org/1751-8121/40/29/017/">journal</a></li>
